question: Tī 2016 nî 12 goe̍h 31 hôe-ki̍t ê chòe tit ê 'chha-choân tit' ê kòe-la̍t sêng-pún, sī B lia̍t tîng-thâu, àn-choân sī E lia̍t tîng-thâu, ê tì chiah khah koân?
answer: The data set starting in column B ($4050 million)

question: 2016 nî cheng-chāi kó͘-sǹg goân-chek ê choán-piàn, giâm-chāi giâm-chāi kó͘-sǹg ê chhù-choè sìⁿ-sò͘ ( tē-saⁿ lia̍t ) ūi-tōe sī siáⁿ-mih ê lô-bōe?

2016 nî 12 goe̍h 31 ji̍t ê chha-chha, chha-chha chha-chha chha-chha chha-chha, lōe khài-liâm chha-chha chha-chha chha-chha chha-chha chha-chha? 'interest income' chha-chha chha-chha chha-chha chha-chha chha-chha chha-chha '-414 ( 414 )' ê sî, 'adjusted EBITDA margin' ê 'as filed' ê chha-chha sī chí-chiáⁿ?
Tī tē 1 ê su-liāu (B-D ê bô͘), 'chhiūⁿ chha̍p-chāi' ê net income kap 'chhiūⁿ chha̍p-chāi' ê adjusted EBITDA ê pí-tùi sī hòⁿ-me, chòe-hōe sann ê sió-sò͘ ūi chòe hòⁿ-me?
Tī B kàu D liâu ê chu-liāu tiong, só͘-chāi ê metric sī che só͘-chāi ê 'as adjusted' ê sòaⁿ ài sió hō͘ 'as filed' ê sòaⁿ?
'Net income as a percentage of service revenue' ê chhek lāi, ūi-sī ê 'change in accounting principle' ê hông-kè tō suah chhin-chhiūⁿ m̄-tú-tio̍h, chin-chiàⁿ ū siáⁿ-mih iân-kù?
answer: C4 kah F4 ê cel lāi ê 'change in accounting principle' hông-kè '2014% ( 2014 % )' chin chhin-chhiūⁿ m̄-tú-tio̍h. Ki-chāi nn̄g ê chu-liāu tūi lóng-chóng, 'net income as a percentage of service revenue' chha-put-to̍h bô piàn, tùi 'as filed' kah 'as adjusted' ê hông-kè lóng sī 5% kàu 5% kah 3% kàu 3%. Nā-sī chin chin-chhiūⁿ ê piàn-tōa, kai èng sī 0%, tō hō͘ '2014%' chin chhián-chhiūⁿ tiâu-chhut, ū khó-lêng sī chu-liāu siá bē chòe chòe ê sài.

question: Nāi-kú `operating income` ê `change in accounting principle` tī tē-jī ê su-liāu-chi̍p, nā-sī kiám-chió 50 pah-bān bí-kim tò-tùi si hián-sī ê kè-ta̍t, hit-tong sî `as adjusted` ê `operating income` ē-sī siáⁿ-mih?
Tī nn̄g lūi chu-liāu lāi, chòe-gia̍h siu-ji̍p (operating income) ê kái-chè kap kiàⁿ ki-khài siu-ji̍p (adjusted EBITDA) ê kái-chè sī ū tīn-tō͘ ê koan-hē--bô?
answer: Ū, sī ū tīn-tō͘ ê tēⁿ-kòe koan-hē. Tī tē it lūi chu-liāu tiong, chòe-gia̍h siu-ji̍p ê kái-chè (+$248) kap kiàⁿ ki-khài siu-ji̍p ê kái-chè (+$248) sī kā-káⁿ--ê. Tī tē jī lūi chu-liāu tiong, chòe-gia̍h siu-ji̍p ê kái-chè (+$414) mā kap kiàⁿ ki-khài siu-ji̍p ê kái-chè (+$414) sī kā-káⁿ--ê. Che chí-chāi kóng, kái-chè hāu-èng tī chòe-gia̍h siu-ji̍p ê kái-chè hāu-èng, chiàu kiàⁿ ki-khài siu-ji̍p sī kā-káⁿ ê liōng kiâⁿ-chham.

question: Tī chit ê piáu-ta̍t ê té-bīn-chū liáu-kái ê sî, siáⁿ chi̍t kiāⁿ tōa ê kò͘-chō hong-bīn ê būn-tê ē chōa bî-lū ê ki-tè?
answer: Siāng tōa ê kò͘-chō hong-bīn būn-tê sī té-bīn-chū bô chi̍t ê koân-koân ê kûn-choán, lâi chē-chē pái chòe kò͘-chú ê té-bīn-chū. Chit ê té-bīn-chū 'year ended december 31 2016 as filed' kah 'year ended december 31 2016 change in accounting principle' tōa-tōa-la̍t-la̍t sú-iōng tī nn̄g khoán bô-kāng ê té-bīn-chū (B kah E; C kah F). Chit ê bî-lūⁿ-sî kàng-sî, ài hō͘ sú-iōng-chiá jīn-ûi sī nn̄g chióng bô-kāng ê tē-ūi ia̍h-sī sî-liâu ê pí-kàu, m̄-koh bô siá chin chhián.

question: Kā 'sòa-tiāu' ê cī uī lâi thó͘ chè, kiám-chhài thó͘ chè nn̄g chióng su-liāu ê siau-sòe sîn-chhiò (Adjusted EBITDA / Adjusted EBITDA margin) chiong nn̄g ê tùi-li̍p chha-pia̍h (tē-it kiat-sòe hō͘ tē-jī kiat-sòe), chòe chīn ê tiâu-chè. , kiám-chhài ēng
Tī siánn-ê chòe-thâu ê sò͘-kì tang-tiong, chòe-thâu ê chòe-gia̍p hòe-li̍h (tī pah-bān gîn-tôaⁿ) tùi 'chòe siū thîⁿ' kàu 'chòe tiâu-chéng' ê sî-chūn, nn̄g-thang tn̂g chē-chē?
